attachments.text: Singer and fashion force Rita Ora was inspired by the exotic world of Japanese geishas when she designed this elegant kimono style. This reversible, wide-cut women's wrap shows off an elegant scenic print on one side and a subtle tonal jacquard pattern on the other. Worn loose or belted, it's a dramatic look with a sporty soul.
